document.body:
In order to view the newsticker, please enable javascript.
Thank you for visiting our new Internet site. As an up-to-date business, we want to give you the opportunity to stay in touch with our company and our offers. A new content management system will enable us to always keep you up to date.
M&M Fish is a locally owned fast food restaurant. M&M Fish is located in South Jackson as an international company through our creative approach to the company's image and detail presentation. At present, our web site is still under construction. We are making an effort to present you with our entire spectrum of offers as soon as possible. If you are not familiar with our company and your first contact with us is online: We would be pleased to hear from you! Please let us know what your suggestions are, we will be more than happy to help.
In brief, you should know the following about us: our company was established in February 2011 and had been responsible for providing outstanding service ever since. Our business is located at 3073 Terry Rd, Jackson, MS 39212.
